headline: One stock that could benefit from market volatility
summary: The stock market has been on a wild ride since the start of 2025. But that doesn't mean investors can't profit. In the video above, CFRA Research chief investment strategist Sam Stovall shares one stock that could benefit from the recent market shakiness.
